<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { background: #050806; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; min-height: 100vh; margin: 0; font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; }
        
        
        .card { width: 700px; background: #0c120f; border-radius: 24px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #1a2a22; }
        
        .image-container { height: 280px; position: relative; cursor: pointer; }
        .image-container img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
        
        .close-btn { position: absolute; top: 15px; right: 15px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6); color: white; border-radius: 50%; width: 32px; height: 32px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; cursor: pointer; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; }
        .vision-tag { position: absolute; bottom: 20px; left: 20px; background: #29b347; color: #000; padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; }
        
        .content { padding: 30px; color: #e0e0e0; }
        h2 { margin: 0 0 15px 0; font-size: 26px; color: #fff; }
        p { color: #a7b8b1; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 25px; }
        
        .meta { display: flex; gap: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: #7a8c85; font-size: 14px; }
        
        .tech-list { display: flex; gap: 10px; }
        .tech-item { border: 1px solid #2d3d37; padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 12px; color: #e0e0e0; }
        
       
        .btn-container { display: flex; justify-content: flex-start; margin-top: 25px; }
        .btn { background: #29b347; color: #000; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 10px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; }
        
        #fullscreen-overlay { display: none; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.95); z-index: 1000; justify-content: center; align-items: center; }



        #fullscreen-overlay img { max-width: 90%; max-height: 90%; border-radius: 15px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="myCard">
    <div class="image-container" onclick="document.getElementById('fullscreen-overlay').style.display='flex'">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1550751827-4bd374c3f58b?q=80&w=1000" alt="Smart Vision">
        <div class="close-btn" onclick="event.stopPropagation(); document.getElementById('myCard').style.display='none'">✕</div>
        <div class="vision-tag">Computer Vision</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Smart Vision Detection</h2>
        <p>Leveraging YOLOv8 and custom-trained models, this system achieves 97.3% accuracy in detecting manufacturing defects. Deployed in partnership with a local factory in Chlef for pilot testing.</p>
        
        <div class="meta"><span>👥 3 members</span> <span>📅 Nov 2025</span></div>

        <div class="tech-list">
            <span class="tech-item">🏷PyTorch</span>
            <span class="tech-item">🏷YOLOv8</span>
            <span class="tech-item">🏷OpenCV</span>
        </div>

        <div class="btn-container">
            <a href="123" class="btn">View Full Project</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div id="fullscreen-overlay" onclick="this.style.display='none'">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1550751827-4bd374c3f58b?q=80&w=1000">
</div>

</body>
</html>